        "timestamp": "2017-11-28 01:22:20.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nTommy, The Amsterdam release has already happened.  The version 4.0.10 cdapbroker has been released as part of the Amsterdam, for which the 4.0.10 git head was tagged with \"amsterdam\".   In preparation for R1.0.1 and R1.0.2 Amsterdam maintenance releases, the code has since also been branched to amsterdam branch.  That is why Jess bumped the version for code at the head of the amsterdam branch, -- 4.0.10 is out so we have to start from the next version.  In other words, we will have 4.0.11, 4.0.12 ... for code on amsterdam branch from now on; and 4.1.0, 4.1.1.... or even 4.2.* or 5.*.* for code on master branch.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
